title: Painter's Palette Tray
description:
Make a masterpiece of your hors d'oeuvres buffet with this unique ceramic tray. Impress your guests by artistically displaying fine cheeses or other tasty delectables. To keep the look authentic, the tray features a rainbow of colors, and even has a thumb-hole! Dishwasher and food safe. 

15 x 11 5/8 in.
